data.u_healthy_life___it___values_: I follow a daily routine, adhere to proper nutrition and balanced physical activity (nutrition and fitness)

data.u_self_develop_l__i___values_: I follow the rules of decency and norms of behavior in society, while always remaining true to my principles (dignity, dedication, fidelity, adnerence to principles)
data.u_self_esteem__al__i___needs_: People respect me for my honesty, integrity and responsibility (Respect)

data.u_self_esteem__al__i___needs_: I have warm relationships with my family, friends and colleagues. I am valued and loved (Relations & authentic connections)

data.u_self_develop_l__i___values_: I am the master of my life and boldly take advantage of available opportunities to protect my interests and get what I want (opportunism)

data.u_self_develop_l__i___values_: I feel alive, I am full of strength and energy. And that's great! (vitality)
data.u_self_esteem__al__i___needs_: Nothing threatens my existence, I'm safe (safety)
